Date: 1996-11-15

Title: Exercises in equivariant cohomology and topological theories

Authors: Raymond Stora

Comments: 17 pages, LaTeX with sprocl.sty, also available at

Equivariant cohomology is suggested as an alternative algebraic framework forthe definition of topological field theories constructed by E. Witten circa1988. It also enlightens the classical Faddeev Popov gauge fixing procedure.